### --- Correderas ---

### Listar correderas
GET {{baseUrl}}/correderas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ver corredera
GET {{baseUrl}}/correderas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear corredera
POST {{baseUrl}}/correderas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Corredera Blum 45kg",
    "capacidad_carga": 45,
    "tipo": "telescopica",
    "incluye_varilla": false,
    "precio_base": 350.00,
    "precio_con_acoplamiento": 420.00
}

### Actualizar corredera
PUT {{baseUrl}}/correderas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Corredera Blum 50kg",
    "capacidad_carga": 50,
    "precio_base": 380.00,
    "precio_con_acoplamiento": 450.00
}

### Eliminar corredera
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/correderas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

