### --- Puertas ---

### Listar puertas
GET {{baseUrl}}/puertas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ver puerta
GET {{baseUrl}}/puertas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear puerta
POST {{baseUrl}}/puertas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Puerta cristal templado",
    "precio_perfil_aluminio": 150.00,
    "precio_escuadras": 80.00,
    "precio_silicon": 20.00,
    "precio_cristal_m2": 250.00,
    "alto_maximo": 2400,
    "ancho_maximo": 600
}

### Actualizar puerta
PUT {{baseUrl}}/puertas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Puerta cristal templado 6mm",
    "precio_cristal_m2": 280.00,
    "alto_maximo": 2500,
    "ancho_maximo": 700
}

### Eliminar puerta
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/puertas/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
